     <h1>About</h1>
     <p>We all know too well that figuring out your schedule at Northwestern can be a pain. CAESAR is slow and makes it difficult to visualize a schedule of courses in real time. This is why we made courseseek. courseseek lets you quickly add and remove classes and immediately see them on a calendar. Switching between lectures and labs or discussion sections helps you find a schedule that works for you. Once you've decided what you want, then you can log on to CAESAR and add them to your shopping cart and be ready to register.

     <br> <br><b>Note</b>: courseseek does not currently support biology classes, as they are formatted slightly different on CAESAR, due to the high number of sections offered. We're working on a solution.</p>
